title: Artist Spotlight: The Caribbean Glitch Art of IX Shells
description: Breaking through the male-dominated NFT art world, IX Shells gets vulnerable with Kevin Rose and her journey from Panama to Canada. She became the highest-selling female NFT artist with the $2 million sale of her artwork "Dreaming at Dusk."
dc:creator: Kevin Rose
